All great things must come to an end, and this pride month will go down in history as one of the best. Good thing I’m gay 365 days a year though 🤷🏼🥳💁🏼 

I’ve had so much fun dancing, vibing, and loving this month with you. Thank you to everyone who’s come out to any of my shows/sets/events. I do this because of y’all and I am so grateful for the love and support I receive from you.

With that being said, I would love for everyone and their mom (if she’s an ally) or their dad (who you can introduce me to tysm) to come out to one of the events this week. Let’s close out pride with the highest of energies 🎉⚡️🧲
